  Anubis Cron Job -- Executor : Schedules/Triggers
  Executor -- TOML Descriptors : Transpiles
  Executor -- Kubernetes (EKS) : Deploys/Monitors
  Executor -- EC2 (Bare Metal) : Deploys/Monitors
  Executor -- SageMaker : Deploys/Monitors
  Executor -- Kafka : Benchmark Events
  Watcher -- Kubernetes (EKS) : Monitors Status
  Watcher -- SageMaker : Monitors Status
  Watcher -- Kafka : Status Updates
  Metrics -- Kafka : Pushes Metrics
  Metrics -- Elasticsearch : Pushes Metrics (Alternative)
  Metrics -- Logs : Extracts Metrics
  CloudWatch Exporter -- Kafka : Extracts Metrics
  CloudWatch Exporter -- CloudWatch : Pushes Metrics
  Fetcher Dispatcher -- Kubernetes (EKS) : Dispatches Fetch Requests as Jobs
  Fetcher Dispatcher -- Puller : Runs jobs for pulls.
  Executor -- Jobs : Creates/Applies
  Executor -- Services : Creates/Applies
  Kubernetes (EKS) -- Jobs : Executes Benchmark Jobs
  Kubernetes (EKS) -- Services : Exposes Services
  Kafka -- CloudWatch Exporter
  Kafka -- Metrics
  CloudWatch -- Grafana : Visualizes Metrics

  note top of Metrics : Includes metrics-pusher & metrics-extractor
  note right of Elasticsearch : Backends for emitting metrics

  [TOML Descriptors] .> [Jobs] : Generates Manifests
  [TOML Descriptors] .> [Services] : Generates Manifests
  [TOML Descriptors] .> [SageMaker] : Generates Job Definitions

}
